{"tid":1786453,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"譚仔雲南米線躋身全球第七美食","createTime":"2019-12-17T07:06:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-21T07:20:01.000Z","uid":1086,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f6c123f922b74e50d78b81726088c831d2dba806","tid":1786453,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T07:06:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2520000/2522033/171219__v1_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2520000%2F2522033%2F171219__v1_1024.jpg&h=6873e456&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n外賣配送平台戶戶送（Deliveroo）表示，回顧過去12個月的顧客訂單，發現最受香港人歡迎的外賣美食是譚仔雲南米線，<span style=\"color: red;\">若綜合全球美食排名，譚仔亦躋身第七位</span>。Deliveroo表示，<span style=\"color: red;\">「譚仔雲南米線的米線+一餸」於過去一年的訂單數目高踞全港榜首，成為港人至愛。</span>其他打入香港十大最愛點選菜式的麵食包括任你點車仔麵的車仔麵 （1麵3餸起）及有緣小敍的五香驢肉Biang Biang麵。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2520000/2522033/1_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2520000%2F2522033%2F1_1024.jpg&h=42e54b81&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">▲ 香港仔譚仔雲南米線的米線+一餸</span><br />\n<br />\n香港人的心水美食：<br />\n1.香港仔譚仔雲南米線的米線+一餸<br />\n2.中環KALE的Kale Salad<br />\n3.中環湯譜的花膠蟲草花螺頭燉湯<br />\n4.九龍城任你點車仔麵的車仔麵 （1麵3餸起）<br />\n5.上環POK&Eacute;WORLD的Sushi Rice Bowl<br />\n6.灣仔戶戶小廚旗下品牌Kai的WASA-BAE<br />\n7.元朗永年士多的豬腸<br />\n8.中環有緣小敍的五香驢肉Biang Biang麵<br />\n9.長沙灣一碗肉燥的很讚紅燒牛肉<br />\n10.中環祥興記上海生煎包的招牌生煎包（4隻）<br />\n在名單上有七款為中港台美食，而麵食佔了中3款。在西式餐點方面，多數港人偏好較為健康的菜式，包括KALE的Kale Salad、POK&Eacute;WORLD的Sushi Rice Bowl以及Kai的WASA-BAE，三款均為主打健康食材、口感輕盈的菜式。<br />\n<br />\n全球十大美食<br />\n1.法國巴黎Pokawa的Pok&eacute; Signature Super Prot&eacute;in&eacute;<br />\n2.英國倫敦Five Guys的芝士漢堡包<br />\n3.巴塞羅那Gonzalez &amp; Co的墨西哥捲餅<br />\n4.意大利米蘭Pok&egrave;ria by NIMA的Salmon Pok&egrave;<br />\n5.愛爾蘭都柏林Subway的Footlong Sub<br />\n6.澳洲吉朗Boss Burger Co的Tommy the Chook<br />\n7.<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港譚仔雲南米線的米線+一餸</span></span></strong><br />\n8.阿聯酋杜拜Shake Shack的Shack Burger<br />\n9.比利時列日Quick的Big Giant Menu<br />\n10.荷蘭阿姆斯特丹Sushito的Sushi Burrito<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2520000/2522033/2_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2520000%2F2522033%2F2_1024.jpg&h=ff2f274f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nDeliveroo表示，以雞肉為材料的美食顯然備受追捧。在今年Deliveroo全球百大美食的排行榜上，選用禽鳥作食材的菜式佔了五分之一。另外，傳統亞洲食品亦深受顧客喜愛，佔了四分之一。"},{"pid":"2a4a0fd283a701ea6474b0dfa9c6c857f1c53438","tid":1786453,"uid":202524,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T07:06:55.000Z","msg":"唔好意思 借個位黎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">德國戰線要人</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">目標：5萬人聯署</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">依家差1萬5千人咋！！！</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇時間啦25號截止，極度要人幫手!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1782422\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1782422</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9d5fe82df8ca48255a6b2d8345ff0eef581a2633","tid":1786453,"uid":71508,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1